#RESTART


setup systemctl service paft.service to auto run paft on restart
1. copy paft.service and mon.service into /usr/lib/systemd/system/
2. systemctl enable paft
3. systemctl enable mon
4. systemctl start paft
5. systemctl start mon
6. systemctl stop mon
7. systemctl stop paft


add to /etc/sudoers
veeru ALL=NOPASSWD: /bin/systemctl restart paft.service


